headline: Home Depot (HD) Lags Q3 Earnings Estimates
summary: Home Depot (HD) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -1.84% and +0.88%, respectively, for the quarter ended October 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
